Thunderstorm: I can go fast enough in jet mode, but 500 kilos is too 
great a load for either chopper or jet mode. I would have to come back 
in assault vehicle mode, which could take considerably longer. All in 
all, I could estimate... a day and a half...

He was not very enthusiastic though. Energon, even if stable, did 
react quite explosively to gunfire. And if he was full of it, a single 
shot could just blow him up.

Thunderstorm: And an escort could be in order. I really don't want to 
get blown to pieces!
